ARCOS data should be amended.

76
00:03:57,250 --> 00:04:02,290
And in fact, they released
data from 2006 to 2012,

77
00:04:02,290 --> 00:04:06,020
and eventually 2014.

78
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:10,020
