285
00:15:36,470 --> 00:15:38,420
However, since they
weren't well-known,

286
00:15:38,420 --> 00:15:40,450
they avoided DEA's
scrutiny for many years.

287
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:46,210
Journalists also
