313
00:17:11,560 --> 00:17:16,232
But the profiteers are huge
that sales didn't slow down,

314
00:17:16,232 --> 00:17:17,690
and we're still
feeling the effects

315
00:17:17,690 --> 00:17:23,087
to this day in a different way.

316
00:17:23,087 --> 00:17:25,670
Prescription pain pills were the
main cause of overdose deaths

317
00:17:25,670 --> 00:17:28,410
through 2011.

318
00:17:28,410 --> 00:17:31,892
But then after the laws were
passed, after pharmacies caught

319
00:17:31,892 --> 00:17:34,350
on, after doctors caught on,
and started restricting access

320
00:17:34,350 --> 00:17:36,990
to prescription pain
pills, drug users

321
00:17:36,990 --> 00:17:42,290
then turned to heroin, which
set the stage for fentanyl.

322
00:17:42,290 --> 00:17:45,110
And together, oxycodone,
hydrocodone, heroin,

323
00:17:45,110 --> 00:17:47,450
and fentanyl have killed
more than 400,000 Americans

324
00:17:47,450 --> 00:17:50,650
since the turn of the
century, a quarter of whom

325
00:17:50,650 --> 00:17:52,800
have died from fentanyl in
just the last six years.

326
00:17:57,040 --> 00:18:00,420
So I'm not exactly sure
how to wrap up this talk,

327
00:18:00,420 --> 00:18:06,550
but I want to point out that I
hope the data that should have

328
00:18:06,550 --> 00:18:10,900
been kept an eye on by
